Package org.tedros.fx.collections

Interface ITObservableList<E>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Collection<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.List<E>, javafx.beans.Observable, javafx.collections.ObservableList<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TSimpleObservableList
    public interface ITObservableList<E>
extends javafx.collections.ObservableList<E>
     This interface type of ObservableList have methods which indicates when the list or your itens are changed.
 
 Important:
 Use the TFXCollections iTObservableList() method to get a proxy instance of this Class, 
 the proxy returned will calculate the property tHashCodeProperty every time the list or a item is changed.
    Author:
    Davis Gordon
    See Also:
    ObservableList
